Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個讓人討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該喜歡讓人來欺負你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這血可是要付出很大的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，把她的雙腿打開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什、什麼？不要，住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼...呀...什麼什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？這個爆炸是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？由紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是野上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來勸告大家快點避難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呀，對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們什麼都不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我不按這個按鈕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...哈哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師！你到底做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎？真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...山田叶子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種人並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟剛才的爆炸一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還埋放在很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個教室也有放置喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法，已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對現在的教育抱持著很多疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對這個腦袋裡只裝著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣或那樣沒有用的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道去怎樣使用的教育方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經很不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢，我要讓你們接受我的特別教育
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人，誰也無法做到的\N我的特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"問明日之道——今天可能會死"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼非要陪你玩這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什麼事你的自由\N但我幹嘛非要參與？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死你自己一個人去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那，那是什麼燈啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是安全裝置的解除警告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要按下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都會毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括現在這個教室，你們想要這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，請不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼，反正是胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈...今天當焦人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚變骨灰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止吧，老師是玩真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是科學部的，真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我不是在胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了，現在時間還很長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我的助手好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上城光也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果老師一定要的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這教室裡還有一位科學部的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了，就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫村野直人，沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你也是助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們像這樣乖乖的聽我的課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別走啊，你以為我會原諒你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了，當我特別課程的教材好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以打她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是常被她欺負嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但，但是，我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道喔，剛才...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，不要，求求你，請住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處女的對象是個拖把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那時村野沒來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺負人家的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也應該讓她感受這種痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？不肯聽我的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不肯聽的話，你也要變我的教材了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，怎麼可以這樣，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔，你也要和我作對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上城，就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...直人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拉我的手，不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要碰山岡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵...友情結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，你也蠻有學問的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是聖經裡的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨阿，我的課現在才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對，先從本井開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了，光也\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是人體...\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村野，這是人體的\N生理構造觀察試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用本井來試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了方便觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要把本井變為裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井，不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然不用剪的東西也會被剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是娃娃\N連身體都是幼兒體型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是第二生長期還沒到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，把內褲拉起一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生是沒有男性的陰莖和睪丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到沒，什麼都沒有附上，知道了嗎\N不要...好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來，本井，把屁股抬高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家好好的看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對，光也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她的內褲脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家好好的看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...大家不要看我...不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在要讓大家看\N女生的排尿組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生沒有陰莖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有個尿道口，裡面有小孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裡排尿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在，用藥來觀察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很強烈的藥，應該馬上生效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託，讓我去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，但是可以用這個來代替
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看，現在本井應該很想排尿才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等呢，本井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...不要啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸說憋尿可是尿道炎的成因喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，大家不要看，不要，啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排了很多尿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井讓我們做了一個不錯的試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我不會像那樣做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下個是用胸部來做觸感的試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...住手，不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣，光也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本井你真的很順從
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是種美德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不愧是一種特別的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼用胸部來做試驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，按摩她的胸部一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣，是不是很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的胸部很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以當一個好教材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你除了欺負本井之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還欺負很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有生命的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個觸覺器官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透過皮膚\N讓體內知道痛的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但胸部大都是脂肪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以對生命是不會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為什麼會那麼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為女生的胸部\N是養育孩子的重要器官之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以常被保護及\N帶有敏感之功能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"為了解除痛的危機"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"快點做保護"以而傳至
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腦的信號很強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不可以停止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其乳頭是\N讓嬰兒喝奶的重要部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最敏感的一個部份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以人體當中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定它是個最發達的觸覺部份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀，我還沒說完就掛了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也叫她醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個重要的試驗\N在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對，把那裡面用你的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好去攪拌它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直給她感覺\N它就逐漸會把痛感忘記的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳到大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腦會命令分泌 荷爾蒙\N將信號轉變為快感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的痛感也就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的構造真的是一流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後那個快感就變成快感中樞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人充滿了生命之感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而感到生命之昂貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人覺得不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂性本能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，再給她的敏感部分\N痛苦一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣，只是痛而已嗎？\N還帶來了快感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，失神了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣是痛還是快感就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生大事件了...喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電視台的直昇機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來全都在我的預料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我告訴他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨吉彥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨你在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的話回話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請同學幫我拉一下窗簾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不願被扔下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師，請你不要做下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼多人你怎能勝過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔...是他們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈不只在校內設置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時還會設置到土地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那些炸彈，把他們引爆的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說校內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連校外也會毀到一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很厲害的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇...怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但對外面的人是要保密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則他們會搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不要讓違規的人出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要去告訴外面的人一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面還有很多人質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然電視台都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要有個強烈的印象才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不要穿衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上城，村野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託，請不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的人也幫忙一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家拜託請不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...不要...不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟山田的胸部大小不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比較起來硬多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我用這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會跟山田一樣變大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是老師說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！不要！\N這邊也弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...不要...不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼要不要跟下面的人\N打招呼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託，不要...很痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託...請不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要...不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇，真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用胸部就可以吊人的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家把繩子提起來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？有沒有跟下面的人\N打招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在問你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請救救我，不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,線在該下半部份的問候了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...這是什麼...\N不要...住手...不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要......
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼...看得一清二楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在緊張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸為我做了些藥膏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要大家好好的看內部的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...不要\N嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得柔軟多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的手你已經無法感受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以用這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...住手...拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不動對我來說是不行的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家好好的問候一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光也，你做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已經不需要我來指示了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以做得很好嘛，由紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但日本的電視台\N可是沒有貞操性的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看，他們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有模糊不清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為剛才我告訴他們\N如果把影像修改的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就立刻用炸彈爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來，由紀子，沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放輕鬆，由紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了，放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班長好像壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，人的精神蠻脆弱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不原諒你們做人的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔，不原諒是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我現在就是對你們這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我現在沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我絕不原諒你們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀，好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不討厭你這樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(待續)